{"tid":2119761,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"林柏特認低威：同紅軍爭好遠","createTime":"2020-07-22T09:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T10:51:39.000Z","uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ca2fe7866b27a2fc2dbe7dec83507cd8f118052f","tid":2119761,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:23:46.000Z","msg":"車路士在周三英超作客硬撼利物浦，領隊林柏特承認兩軍有一大段差距。<br />\n<br />\n進入今場之前，車路士以36戰63分排第3位，足足比冠軍利物浦少30分，林柏特（Frank Lampard）也坦言兩軍之間有一段距離：「我們要現實一點，兩支球隊正處於不同的位置，但我們有目標。」<br />\n<br />\n車仔跟紅軍的差別，其中一樣相信是穩定性，林伯表示：「我不會歸咎於陣容年輕，但的確有關係。當我們勝出時，所有事看來都很好。我們要看遠一點，複製出擊敗曼聯時的心態。」 <br />\n<br />\n雖然淘汰紅魔殺入英足盃，但林柏特直言保住英超前4才是今季首要目標：「出戰歐聯代表了球隊的名聲及現時的位置。今季是這是最多考驗的一季，必須努力收窄差距。我們還未真正回來。」"},{"pid":"4547031b0bb9f4368a6b3378255312792a79c71d","tid":2119761,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:33:53.000Z","msg":"利可以踢風流波<br />\n<br />\n梗係認下衰仔先啦"},{"pid":"df03300282bee1114810f77a03423a34d6259929","tid":2119761,"uid":103207,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"4547031b0bb9f4368a6b3378255312792a79c71d","tid":2119761,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:33:53.000Z","msg":"利可以踢風流波<br />\n<br />\n梗係認下衰仔先啦"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:59:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dC43VEx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdC43VEx.png&h=44085b95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZHBYKxS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZHBYKxS.png&h=13b24c77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官方唔係咁睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac877efd3b9ec34d02fbdd5bd686ecde0d550e5d","tid":2119761,"uid":204475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df03300282bee1114810f77a03423a34d6259929","tid":2119761,"uid":103207,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"4547031b0bb9f4368a6b3378255312792a79c71d","tid":2119761,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike"